start mongodb--

> sudo systemctl start mongodb
> sudo systemctl stop mongodb
	or
> sudo systemctl restart mongodb


check mongodb service status
> sudo systemctl status mongodb
 

mongodb install on windows 10
--------------------------

follow the link

https://medium.com/@LondonAppBrewery/how-to-download-install-mongodb-on-windows-4ee4b3493514


For those who are on windows and want to add mongo alias:
Search for environment variables in windows search and go to path and add a new path `C:\Program Files\MongoDB\Server\4.0\bin`
Now restart terminal

run,
> mongo


